                    This abbreviated CV was generated by the UAlberta Faculty of Science science forum system to meet the requirement of UAlbertaâ€™s {$next_year} Quality Assurance Graduate and Undergraduate Program Review. Information is reported for the period July 1 {$startYear} to June 30 {$endYear} only and does not reflect the full academic record of the staff member.
                </div>
                <br />
                <br />
                <br />
                <br />
                <br />
                <br />
